50|$|It {{is home to}} the endemic race ornatus of the {{red bush}} squirrel, the endemic race woodwardi of Woodward's barbet, two undescribed <b>dwarf</b> <b>chameleons</b> similar to the Qudeni dwarf chamaeleon, the rare forest green {{butterfly}} and the oNgoye centipede.|$|E
